snippet.title: Mission Zero | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Agents, are you ready for this mission? The first round of the Technical Test is coming! 

Pre-register now:  https://www.missionzero.game/

-------Technical Test Info ---------
- Test Time: Start from July 8th 2022(Time to complete the test: TBD)
- Test Region: Thailand、Malaysia、Australia、New Zealand
- Test Platform: PC and Android

For more information, please follow:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Missionzerogame
Discord: https://discord.gg/tQZTBYwgRC
